### Weather Image App - API Documentation
### Base URL: http://localhost:7071 (local) or https://your-function-app.azurewebsites.net (Azure)
### Authentication: X-API-Key header required for all endpoints

### 1. Test Image Processing (Single Station)
### Generates a weather image for one random weather station
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test/image
X-API-Key: dev-weather-app-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Start Job (All 36 Stations)
### Initiates image processing for all weather stations
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/job/start
X-API-Key: dev-weather-app-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Get Job Status
### Retrieves the status and results of a job
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/job/{{jobId}}
X-API-Key: dev-weather-app-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Example Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071
@jobId = your-job-id-here
@apiKey = dev-weather-app-key-12345
